Ext.data.JsonP['SplitWindow']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>SplitWindow</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-41845771\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>SplitWindow</h1>\n    <p>Demonstrates how to use a SplitWindow control, an iPad-only control for managing the presentation of two views in a master-detail UI.    </p>\n    <div class=\"confbox admonition admonition-info aui-message hint shadowed information-macro has-no-icon\">\n            <div class=\"title\">App Folder Location</div>\n            <p>alloy/test/apps/<strong class=\" \">ui/splitwindow</strong>    </p>\n    </div>\n        <img src=\"images/download/attachments/41845771/ipad.png\" alt=\"images/download/attachments/41845771/ipad.png\" class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" width=\"550\">\n        <p>The &lt;<a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.iPad.SplitWindow\">SplitWindow</a>/&gt; element expects two &lt;<a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.Window\">Window</a>/&gt; elements as children. The first declared &lt;Window/&gt; is the &quot;master&quot; view&apos; and the second is the &quot;detail&quot; view. If a &lt;Require&gt; element is used to insert a Window, as in the sample, the required XML view must contain only one top-level element under the &lt;Alloy&gt; tag and that element must be a <a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.Window\">Ti.UI.Window</a> object.    </p>\n    <div class=\"confbox programlisting defaultnew syntaxhighlighter scroll-html-formatted-code\">\n                    <div class=\"title\">views/index.xml</div>\n                <div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" class=\"defaultnew syntaxhighlighter scroll-html-formatted-code\" data-title=\"views/index.xml\">\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">&lt;Alloy&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">  &lt;SplitWindow platform=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;ios&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\"> formFactor=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;tablet&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    &lt;!-- The </code><code class=\"string\">&apos;masterView&apos;</code><code class=\"plain\"> window, added via &lt;Require&gt; tag --&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    &lt;Require src=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;master&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    </code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    &lt;!-- The </code><code class=\"string\">&apos;detailView&apos;</code><code class=\"plain\"> window, using an explicit &lt;Window&gt; tag --&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    &lt;Window&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;Label&gt;This is the detail&lt;/Label&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    &lt;/Window&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">  &lt;/SplitWindow&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">&lt;/Alloy&gt;</code></div>\n</div>\n    </div>\n    <p>The &quot;master&quot; view consists of &lt;<a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.TabGroup\">TabGroup</a>/&gt; element with two &lt;<a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.Tab\">Tab</a>/&gt; child elements.    </p>\n    <div class=\"confbox programlisting defaultnew syntaxhighlighter scroll-html-formatted-code\">\n                    <div class=\"title\">views/master.xml</div>\n                <div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" class=\"defaultnew syntaxhighlighter scroll-html-formatted-code\" data-title=\"views/master.xml\">\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">&lt;Alloy&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">  &lt;TabGroup&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    &lt;Tab title=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;tab 1&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;Window title=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;tab 1&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">        &lt;Label&gt;tab </code><code class=\"value\">1</code><code class=\"plain\">&lt;/Label&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;/Window&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    &lt;/Tab&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    &lt;Tab title=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;tab 2&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;Window title=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;tab 2&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">        &lt;Label&gt;tab </code><code class=\"value\">2</code><code class=\"plain\">&lt;/Label&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">      &lt;/Window&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    &lt;/Tab&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">  &lt;/TabGroup&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">&lt;/Alloy&gt;</code></div>\n</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-41845771_SplitWindow-SeeAlso\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>See Also</span></h2>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.iPad.SplitWindow\">Titanium.UI.iPad.SplitWindow</a> API reference    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.TabGroup\">Titanium.UI.TabGroup</a> API reference    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.Tab\">Titanium.UI.Tab</a> API reference    </p>\n</li></ul>    <p>    </p>\n    </div>\n        </img></div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=41845771\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"SplitWindow"});